question","created":1738897017,"answer_count":112,"follower_count":247,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1398,2276,11422,105508,112504],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"近日，一条关于“京东外卖以只抽5%的佣金的旗号上线，美团降低高佣金应对”的帖子，在多个社交媒上传播。 美团方面表示，网传的关于美团外卖30%的高佣金率数据不实，美团外卖实际商户佣金率为6%～8%。另有知情人士透露，京东涉及餐饮外卖的业务在2024年已经上线，具体收取的佣金比美团外卖略低或者持平。 2024年全国餐饮收入5.57万亿元，增长5.3%，餐饮外卖市场也还在保持增长。民以食为天，餐饮外卖也是高频的刚需消费，目前餐饮外卖市场已有美团和饿了么两大巨头，美团占据绝对的市场优势定位，又一巨头的加入，对外卖市场竞争格局是否能产生撼动？京东为什么要做餐饮外卖生意？详见:https://m.21jingji.com/article/20250206/herald/e7da478b6f008834019dd90159f71813.html"},"attached_info":"CkII0ryRvu/3p44XEAMaCTExMzI3ODEzNCD57JW9BjAAOPcBQBZyCzExNTExNjkwMTc4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"52 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2a1d66552fc8149c301f0f600c548618_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"23_1739355584.710067","card_id":"Q_11915449278","target":{"id":11915449278,"title":"美国科学院院刊显示，朱经武院士团队首次实现 BST 高压超导相结构的常压室温稳定，其研究有哪些价值？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/11915449278","type":"question","created":1739258877,"answer_count":18,"follower_count":98,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2253,98799,2565056,3499949],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"美国科学院院刊（PNAS）2025年2月4日发布的论文显示，朱经武院士团队使用新开发的压力淬火方案（Pressure-Quench Protocol, PQP），首次实现了从金刚石压砧室中室温回收压力淬火样品，且压力诱导的Bi₀.₅Sb₁.₅Te₃（BST）超导相在室温常压的条件下得以保留。 文章链接如下（需复制到浏览器地址栏） https://www.pnas.org/doi/abs/10.1073/pnas.2423102122 --- 论文标题及作者团队 --- “重要性声明”里确实写的是“常压”（ambient pressure）和“室温”（room temperature）。 重要性声明（机翻）： 如著名材料科学家Pol Duwez所言，几乎所有对工业至关重要的固体均处于亚稳态。例如，目前所有超导转变温度的最高记录均仅存在于高压下的材料中，即亚稳态材料。然而，极端条件严重阻碍了对这些亚稳态相的深入探索以及超导潜力的全面释放。解决之道在于将其稳定于常压环境。本研究利用近期开发的压力淬火方案，成功将Bi₀.₅Sb₁.₅Te₃中压力诱导的超导态稳定于常压及室温条件下。这一成果标志着极端条件产生的亚稳态向常压科学应用迈出了关键一步，为未来科学与技术中新型亚稳态的常压保留提供了重要参考。"},"attached_info":"CkEI0ryRvu/3p44XEAMaCTExMzM1ODkxNiD996u9BjAAOGJAF3ILMTE5MTU0NDkyNzh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"50 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a68f4156a881634dfe2c31bd8f7514cc_1440w.jpeg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"24_1739355584.711174","card_id":"Q_11865906428","target":{"id":11865906428,"title":"大学期末改卷老师真的像网上说的那样捞人吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/11865906428","type":"question","created":1739212370,"answer_count":52,"follower_count":71,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2029,21847,136885,1425254,1978990],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"总是看到网上发表的大学生期末老师捞人捞得焦头烂额，为了让学生及格不择手段（写解给分，黑笔改答案，平时分拉满），真的有网上说的那样抽象吗？"},"attached_info":"CkEI0ryRvu/3p44XEAMaCTExMzM0ODk4MyDSjKm9BjAAOEdAGHILMTE4NjU5MDY0Mjh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"48 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7b08e80babb61d08999788763083f599_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"25_1739355584.711531","card_id":"Q_9234247312","target":{"id":9234247312,"title":"牛肉炖什么，怎么炖才好吃？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/9234247312","type":"question","created":1736490718,"answer_count":22,"follower_count":88,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[127032,140989,255342,306598,781389],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"牛肉怎么处理？"},"attached_info":"CkAI0ryRvu/3p44XEAMaCTExMjgyMzQ0MSDe/YK8BjAAOFhAGXIKOTIzNDI0NzMxMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"47 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","t